"      Ramos-Casals M, Brito-Zer&oacute;n P, Sis&oacute;-Almirall A, et al. Topical and systemic medications for the treatment of primary Sj&ouml;gren's syndrome. Nat Rev Rheumatol 2012; 8:399.",
"     </a>",
