"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Upper gastrointestinal series showing nonspecific dilatation of small bowel loops (thin arrow) with a stricture in the duodenal loop (thick arrow) in a patient with secondary amyloidosis.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
